{"tid":177491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]AI無人機的航空母艦？美帝亞馬遜要打造「空中物流中心」","createTime":"2017-03-29T01:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T08:43:09.000Z","uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb232032d89c9e73827f85a2cbcf7583be8c6af","tid":177491,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/29173542/amazon-afc-1-624x429.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F29173542%2Famazon-afc-1-624x429.png&h=f97d9c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜在 2013 年時，就對外公布對於實現無人機送貨的野心，不久前也申請了防劫機的無人機專利，而近日，亞馬遜又申請了另一項新專利，這項新專利就像是要作為無人機的航空母艦一般，專利內容為「空中物流中心（airbone fulfillment centers，AFCs）利用無人機運送商品」，要幫助亞馬遜實現無人機送貨的商用規模物流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/vkyodkxjsjblibtqqqsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fvkyodkxjsjblibtqqqsq.jpg&h=0bdd102b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAFC 系統的角色定位如其名一般，就像是可在空中移動的物流中心，亞馬遜計畫在其內先放進一定數量的存貨，依照用戶需求，選擇合適的空中位置安放飛船，但飛船基本上都會維持在約 4.5 萬英呎的高空，再利用停放在裡頭的無人機，負責運送貨物到指定的送貨地點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/29173729/amazon-afc-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F29173729%2Famazon-afc-2.png&h=46365b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在專利內容敘述中，亞馬遜也舉了一個應用例子來做說明。假如在某個大型場館中，即將舉行足球或棒球這類大型運動賽事的冠軍賽，場內滿滿的人潮，這時亞馬遜的空中物流中心，就能載運著零食或紀念品等，利用無人機來做運送，最直接地滿足球迷的需求。此外，AFC 系統也可在場館附近，提供大型活動的戶外廣告投放服務。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/zcffbuibvoylilmafjwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fzcffbuibvoylilmafjwf.jpg&h=2d9225d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了空中物流中心與無人機外，這項專利中也提及了將運用大型飛梭（shuttle），協助載運人力、貨物或無人機往返空中物流中心，如此一來，也能大大幫助無人機節省電力，使無人機能夠專注於運送貨物上，且當飛梭與無人機在空中運送貨物時，還能互相傳送分享天氣、風速與路線等數據。<br />\n<br />\n目前亞馬遜還未對外透露 AFC 確切的測試或營運時間，但要在空中部署這種空中物流中心，還有許多細節與因素須作考量，不過，一旦 AFC 系統正式上線營運，或許會為亞馬遜的物流服務帶來顛覆性的改變。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ecofriend.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/airbialead_02_7bd4s_5638_zfbkd_n3urm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecofriend.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F08%2Fairbialead_02_7bd4s_5638_zfbkd_n3urm.jpg&h=3498d9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popsci.com/sites/popsci.com/files/styles/large_1x_/public/import/2013/images/2013/06/FOF_airship.jpg?itok=QoxBo0hH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popsci.com%2Fsites%2Fpopsci.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge_1x_%2Fpublic%2Fimport%2F2013%2Fimages%2F2013%2F06%2FFOF_airship.jpg%3Fitok%3DQoxBo0hH&h=d3e331e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wiredcosmos.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/airship-rendering.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwiredcosmos.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F11%2Fairship-rendering.jpeg&h=b36555ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nConsidering the fact that airships have been around for a while now, it&rsquo;s hard to believe that they are thought of as emerging technologies today. But that&rsquo;s exactly the case given recent advances in this arena. Hydrogen airships have a troubled history due to several significant historical disasters. However, new technologies could help reduce this risk drastically.<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/mvdrjcwanzmqolzpckoc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fmvdrjcwanzmqolzpckoc.jpg&h=4a0e41ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA Closer Look<br />\nHelium is a resource that&rsquo;s starting to run low. On the other hand, any industrialized country can cheaply manufacture all the hydrogen it could ever need. In fact, hydrogen is a byproduct of some industrial processes. This means that researchers are turning to it as a cheap lifting gas. The benefits of hydrogen airships might outweigh the perceived risks, and they produce relatively little pollution. In some ways, airships are actually much safer than jet aircraft.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/gltuwgkuabiaaoqxzvcn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fgltuwgkuabiaaoqxzvcn.jpg&h=2764518c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/dtcwosdnugpysoqafwew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fdtcwosdnugpysoqafwew.jpg&h=955dc26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/thlwfujeopdmpdovdeum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fthlwfujeopdmpdovdeum.jpg&h=51264027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.777a7.com/img115/epxrmrpiqeqrdhjlnyjh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.777a7.com%2Fimg115%2Fepxrmrpiqeqrdhjlnyjh.jpg&h=a25628d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4b19b4903a22ee28cbd6ac9214d434dc9e690bb","tid":177491,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"大陸一早試過啦"},{"pid":"6da7ba68e43454015741698c4d68888356200c9b","tid":177491,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸一早試過啦</blockquote><br />\nCG?"},{"pid":"b5d4d580bebb38f8de85fdc482ea26384efb098f","tid":177491,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大陸一早試過啦</blockquote><br />\nCG?</blockquote><br />\n唔知順豐定邊間用無人機送貨"},{"pid":"9540436ac1cfe230285a14ed59d03b5a228f4a70","tid":177491,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大陸一早試過啦</blockquote><br />\nCG?</blockquote><br />\n唔知順豐定邊間用無人機送貨</blockquote><br />\nAI無人航空母艦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/n